messages.message: it was still 10-15 seconds that time for each request

@Anant Don’t have latency requirement but I can ask. Does improved infra sizing help with improving latency? Right now it takes 2 days for a loan officer realize that a customer has submitted an incorrect doc so if it’s a matter of seconds it may not be that big of a deal for them.

@Anant BofA is discussing that question with their client, but for right now they are looking at 5-10 sec. they’re asking if we can provide scaled options so the client can better make cost/benefit decision, but the max should be 30 sec.
